{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九章\"杀\"讲述萧秋水在中毒状态下反杀余氏三兄弟（余不笑、余笑不笑、余我吾），展现了当机立断的侠者之风。文鬓霜赞其有大侠之风，却在随后为替兄弟黄远庸报仇冲入古严关，被瘟疫人魔余哭余以毒术杀害。汉四海率柳千变、屠滚、长天五剑、狮公虎婆等大批追兵从后方赶到，前有余哭余布毒封关，后有强敌环伺，萧秋水等人陷入绝境。关键时刻，汉四海以赌杀为名，暗中以百口长针射杀余哭余，随即揭露真实身份——他不姓汉而姓唐，名为唐朋。唐方与其一唱一和，点破\"汉唐都是盛世\"、\"四海之内皆兄弟\"的暗语。此章以连环反转为核心，展现了权力帮内部的尔虞我诈，以及唐朋深不可测的武功与心机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_bu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "余不笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瘟疫人魔的东西，他都有胆接，死了，也是敢死鬼。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_bu_xiao",
      "speaker_name": "余笑不笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他已经死了，你们谁要跟他去就过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wo_wu",
      "speaker_name": "余我吾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瘟疫一至，鬼哭神号；瘟疫一过，万物无生——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "文鬓霜",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "萧少侠在一公亭把断腿的彭九饶而不杀，是大侠之仁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "文鬓霜",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "而今瞬间诛杀三凶，只因这三个毒人滥杀无辜，确不可饶，决意要杀，绝不容情，此乃侠者之风。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "文鬓霜",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "难得萧少侠年纪颇轻，却有大侠之风，而当机立断，胆大心细，城府深沉，今后武林，必有他这一位不可多得的人才。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀得好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘声音",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "杀得不好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪个王八？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "是我，你们的索命人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么人？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "我是瘟疫，我在哪里，那里就有瘟疫。",
      "tone": "阴森",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "文鬓霜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瘟疫人魔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣人",
      "listener": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "text": "余哭余。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_wen_bin_shuang",
      "text": "文前辈……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我跟你们不同。你们是拿刀拿剑去拼，我有我的毒物跟你们拼。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我在古严关布下了毒，你们过得来，就杀得了我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘青年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你冲过去也没有用，——因为你们已经不必冲过去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "汉四海！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "正是在下。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "speaker_name": "柳千变",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有在上！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_gun",
      "speaker_name": "屠滚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "更有者子！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "你们这可谓'前无去路，后有追兵'。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "君不闻'天无绝人之路'？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "那你们就试走走看吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "后退既无希望，只好前冲了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "要前冲，就得过古严关。",
      "tone": "阴森",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_gun",
      "speaker_name": "屠滚",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "这人要留给我，他暗算了老子一掌。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_gun",
      "speaker_name": "屠滚",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "我要他后悔为什么要生出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "speaker_name": "柳千变",
      "listener": "char_tang_fang",
      "text": "那女的倒要留给我。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "狮公",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "萧秋水留给我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_po",
      "speaker_name": "虎婆",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "我们要把他撕开来吃了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看你们年纪轻轻，却有那么多人恨之入骨，我也没有办法。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zuo_qiu_chao_ran",
      "speaker_name": "左丘超然",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "你少来假惺惺！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "余者兄，看来这几个人是要往你那儿冲，你一人在那儿，要不要多我一个作伴？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "汉兄肯来，欢迎之至。只不过古严关不易渡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "那没什么。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "text": "这儿就全仗诸位了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "speaker_name": "柳千变",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "汉兄放心，保管一个不漏！",
      "tone": "陪笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "text": "有劳诸位了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "好轻功！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "是真的好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "当然是好。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "不见得吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "其实在我翻过墙头时，余兄心里是在想：这小子实在大狂了；要不是看我跟柳五总管有交情，而且又是屈剑王介绍来的，你早就要毒我一毒，给我点厉害瞧瞧了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "不知我说的对不对？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "汉兄大多疑了吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "这样好了，为使余兄心服，我们一齐来赌一赌。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "赌什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "杀那一班人，你用毒，我用暗器。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "如此甚好。只不知你要何种赌法？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "赌杀人，看准杀得快，看谁杀得多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "speaker_name": "余哭余",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "什么时候开始？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "现在。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蛊毒！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_yu_ku_yu",
      "text": "我赢了，我先杀了一个。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "现在前有去路了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_gun",
      "speaker_name": "屠滚",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "汉四海你——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_tu_gun",
      "text": "我不叫汉四海。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "speaker_name": "柳千变",
      "listener": "char_han_si_hai",
      "text": "你是……？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "text": "我不姓汉，我姓唐。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_fang",
      "speaker_name": "唐方",
      "listener": "char_liu_qian_bian",
      "text": "汉唐都是盛世。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_si_hai",
      "speaker_name": "汉四海",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四海之内皆兄弟也。我也不叫四海。",
      "tone": "大笑",
